\par
"two distinct approaches for answering statistical questions: one that is spontaneous, intuitive, effortless, and fast, and another that is deliberate, rule-governed, effortful, and slow" (\href{zotero://open-pdf/library/items/HAVUCCPF?page=3}{Kahneman and Frederick 2002:51})
