\textbf{"found that aesthetic appeal and novelty predict users' levels of attention and involvement in the interaction, and perceptions of the system's usability and endurability of the experience. Endurability refers to individuals' evaluation of the system as worthwhile and rewarding, and their desire to engage with it in future or recommend it to others (O'Brien \& Toms, 2010)." (\href{zotero://open-pdf/0_A6PZUSLP/2}{O'Brien 2017:2810})}
