\par
"The relationship between information overload and purchase intention" (\href{zotero://open-pdf/0_KZLN367W/5}{Soto-Acosta et al 2014:547})
\par
"With regard to the internet several studies have analysed the relationship between information load and decision quality (Chen et al., 2009; Huang, 2000; Sicilia and Ruiz, 2010)." (\href{zotero://open-pdf/0_KZLN367W/5}{Soto-Acosta et al 2014:547})
